   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="writingSession" n="1"><opener><dateline rend="right"><pb facs="Wienbibliothek_AS_FS_2822968"/><date when="1901-09-16">16. <subst><del rend="overwritten">1</del><add place="inline">9</add></subst>. 901</date></dateline></opener><p><salute>Lieber Freund,</salute> der kleine Herr <anchor type="commentary" xml:id="K_L02970-1"/><rs type="person" ref="#pmb2959" cert="low">Lanz</rs><note type="commentary" corresp="K_L02970-1"><rs type="person" ref="#pmb2959">Adolf Lantz</rs>?</note>, der Ihnen <anchor type="commentary" xml:id="K_L02970-2"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>. Z.<note type="commentary" corresp="K_L02970-2">seiner Zeit</note> einige Manu<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>cripte überreicht laßt Sie
               durch mich bitten, diese Manuscripte bei Ihrem <rs type="person" ref="#pmb143364" subtype="implied">Hausmei<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ter</rs> zu <subst><del rend="strikethrough">über</del><add place="above">hinter</add></subst>legen, wo er<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ie<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ich abholen möchte. –</p><p>Warum hab ich Sie a<unclear>uch</unclear><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><anchor type="commentary" xml:id="K_L02970-3"/><date when="1901-09-14">Sam<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>tag</date><note type="commentary" corresp="K_L02970-3"><ref type="schnitzler-briefe" target="L02968" subtype="Cf"/>.
               </note> nicht ge<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ehen? Sollten<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ie<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>chon im <rs type="org" ref="#pmb169320" subtype="implied">Club</rs><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><pb facs="Wienbibliothek_AS_FS_2822969"/>gewe<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>en<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ein? –</p><p>Ich<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>chreibe <anchor type="commentary" xml:id="K_L02970-4"/><rs type="work" ref="#pmb29873 #pmb29877" subtype="implied">2 Einakter</rs><note type="commentary" corresp="K_L02970-4"><rs type="work" ref="#pmb29873">Der Puppenspieler</rs> und <rs type="work" ref="#pmb29877">Die letzten Masken</rs>, <ref type="schnitzler-tagebuch" target="1901-09-16" subtype="cf"/>.</note>, die zu den <rs type="work" ref="#pmb29869 #pmb29865 #pmb29957" subtype="implied">3 andren</rs> gehören.</p><closer>Herzlich<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>t Ihr <lb/><signed>ArthSch</signed></closer></div>
      </body>
